This page was regenerated on the evening of 2026-07-17 after the repair
and cleanup efforts landed — per its own rule: fresh verdicts, not
patched sentences. When the memory system changes materially again
(acting re-flip, soul launch, orphan onboarding), regenerate from a
fresh survey. Receipts:

